        {
            "title": "鳴鳴很忙首掛高收逾69% 每日賬賺1.634萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地連鎖零食商鳴鳴很忙(01768)股份今早掛牌，全日均大幅高於招股價236.6元，收報400元，較招股價高69.06%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"鳴鳴很忙官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/MM-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"鳴鳴很忙官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/MM-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">鳴鳴很忙官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以該股1手100股計，認購並獲配每手賬面賺1.634萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股今早高開88.08%，以445元開市，其後升幅收窄，最低報399.2元，仍高於招股價68.72%；全日成交達33.12億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15619565-%e9%b3%b4%e9%b3%b4%e5%be%88%e5%bf%99%e9%a6%96%e6%8e%9b%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6%e9%80%be69-%e6%af%8f%e6%97%a5%e8%b3%ac%e8%b3%ba1-634%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/MM-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 16:39:04",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市︱恒指升699點報27826點 六連升累漲1339點 資源股強 中資電信股湧上",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股午後再上層樓，且有成交重越3000億元配合升勢。多個主要板塊均揚升，資源股固然強勢畢現，中資電信股亦從後趕上。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今日全程報升，於初段出現的低位27258點時仍升131點，早市明顯呈一浪高於一浪的走勢，半日已漲近600點；午後反覆，不斷刷新4年多的日中高位紀錄，整個午市大部份時間在27700點之上窄幅徘徊。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指以全日高位收市，報27826點，漲699點或2.58%，成功做出六連升的成績，累計共漲1339點或5.06%。恒生科技指數全日也升145點或2.53%，報5900點；國企指數升267點或2.89%，報6512點。主板成交增至3615.23億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15619521-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87699%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b127826%e9%bb%9e-%e5%85%ad%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%87%e7%b4%af%e6%bc%b21339%e9%bb%9e-%e8%b3%87%e6%ba%90%e8%82%a1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-5.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 16:22:40",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "差估署 : 私人樓宇指數連升7個月",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">差餉物業估價署數據顯示，2025年12月全港私人住宅樓價指數升至298.6，按月升0.23%，連升7個月。2025年全年升3.25%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中小型單位(100平方米以下)售價指數按月升0.23%；較大面積單位(100平方米或以上)售價指數按月升0.22%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">當中，A類物業(40平方米以下)售價指數按月升0.03%；B類物業(40至69.9平方米)按月升0.31%；C類物業(70至99.9平方米)按月升0.5%；D類物業(100至159.9平方米)按月升0.07%；E類物業(160平方米或以上)按月升0.71%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">租金指數方面，2025年12月私人住宅租金指數升至200.7，按月升0.1%。2025年全年升4.26%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15618328-%e5%b7%ae%e4%bc%b0%e7%bd%b2-%e7%a7%81%e4%ba%ba%e6%a8%93%e5%ae%87%e6%8c%87%e6%95%b8%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%877%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240726_PP_PROPERTY_INDEX_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 15:39:15",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
